To reduce the use of storage and data transmissions we will cache posts
when we find post data we will access the database first to see if the post exists or not
generally the post will not be stored unless it is
a ReplyTo
a Response
a mention,
a recently seen posts
and saved posts
to recently seen posts would be put into a temp cache
that will be deleted after some time
while the others can be stored in database.

